Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值日要說的就這些 還有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做的可爾必思是不是太淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還嫌濃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}窮人款可爾必思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼窮人款啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:46.23,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可爾必思就是太濃才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}負責的解釋下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呃…飲料是昨天的負責人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會好好處理的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家都說風很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掃廁所！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:14.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\b0\fs35\1c&H544D46&\pos(678,206)}距離夏季隊回國還有{\1c&H6C53A4&\fs55}3{\1c&H544D46&\fs35}天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都說過不愛吃羊栖菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別任性了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我聽說你經常貧血的 保奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女高中生剛來的時候還很可愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家現在又沒在念書
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太習慣南極生活 會很難回歸社會的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}七條胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立一發全純三色雙寶牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 雙裏寶牌就是三倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.79,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都叫你別信筋牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得那是另一種情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽到吸塵器的聲音 就感覺在家裡似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家邀請我去取材了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\b0\fs30\1vc(&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&,&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&)\3c&HE6E9E6&\frz332.1\pos(760,292)}島內散步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.68,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\b0\bord0\fs30\1c&HE1E5DC&\frz332.1\pos(660,470)}洞窟探險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在島上散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和報瀨昨天也被帶出去散步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼不跟我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天要值日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被排擠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}島上散步又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等一下要去Ice Operation呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(745,650)}採雪任務
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對喔 要抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}馬上就到集合時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ice Operation是全員參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\b0\fs25\1vc(&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&,&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&)\3c&HE6E9E6&\pos(700,280)\frz346.9\frx340\fry2}島內散步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\b0\bord0\fs25\1c&HE1E5DC&\frz336.7\frx358\fry4\pos(662,470)}洞窟探險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們四位將前往Ice Operation 請講
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要搭乘哪個才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好壯觀啊 是冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是在鑿這麼大的冰山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極禁止帶出任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是唯一可以帶回去留作紀念的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡的冰塊 密封了幾萬年前的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}融化的時候會劈劈啪啪地裂開來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是幾萬年前空氣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你吃得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我長大要拿它下酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺你喝醉就會吵死人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這項工程一開始我就覺得 夏天要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就是秋天 又是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就要過冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬天都會做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多事呢 玩遊戲啊喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然 做研究和觀測也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只可惜6月後 整天都會是夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就叫永夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有午前的地平線上 會有一絲光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一整天只會有這點變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他時候就只有漫長的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直都是夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過也正因此 讓星空美不勝收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還能看到極光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}極光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說還沒看過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為現在夜晚很短暫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與企鵝拍紀念照 吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但極光和南極星還沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說了因為是永晝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但好幸福 但也好臭 但又好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.93,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好臭 好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回去工作了 你們好好放鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天是你們最後看冰海的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫你救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不能靠近5公尺以內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想點辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們已經習慣這裡的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有這裡的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假設啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是假設
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正房間空著也是空著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這裡也能隨時發影片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以也不用現在立刻回程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你肯定是要整我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會的不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在不回去就只能等明年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道啊 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有信心天黑的時候能一直睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不上學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到時候我們回去 其他人都畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結的電視劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我也有點不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你還會來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要在這裡過冬 四個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說好了啊 不許拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在很認真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也很認真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來 現在怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得隊長說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後有什麼想做的 要跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 最後我們想和這裡的人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:23.79,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}帰り道に並んだ足音が歪んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:29.92,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}あの日と今日　違いすぎた道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:40.73,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}喉の奥に詰まるような　くすんだ視界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}吸い込んで吐いたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.78,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}いつはじまりはこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.20,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}どこまでも続くこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:58.20,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}遠く遠く　見たことない景色へ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:04.17,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}One step One step One step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:23.79,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}一起回家的腳步聲 變得有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:29.92,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}今天與那天的我們 走了不一樣的路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:40.73,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}景色有些暗淡 如同骨鯁在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:44.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}深吸一口氣 再呼出這口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.78,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出這一步 就是啟程的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.20,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}邁出下一步 我們將走遍四方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:58.20,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}向遠方 向遠方 向陌生的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:04.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}一步又一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打個好球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}藤姐加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.04,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長 要是我能打中 你能再考慮一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一言既出！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他還不死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他會打中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟的外號可是「南極豎條紋19號」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:40.10,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※暗指阪神虎隊球衣。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她投出的球是一流的 而且！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有人能躲過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心 貴子還是打中了她投的球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在才剪頭髮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要剪就在來的時候剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然想剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來剪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理 你退後點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要剪多短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.05,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\fs60\1c&HD6B780&\rnd5\blur3\t(0,500,0\blur0)\move(396,356,396,62,0,689)}夏季隊{\1c&H777271&}辛苦了{\1c&H6F3B97&}！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要磨到什麼時候 人家真的要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.02,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\fs30\1c&H8C7668&\frx338\fry332\frz345\move(428,590.001,425.333,161.333,23,1942)}南極挑戰女高中生記者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\fs30\1c&H8C7668&\frx338\fry332\frz345\move(425.334,156,426.667,-270,23,1942)}南極挑戰女高中生記者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\1c&H8A898D&\frz329.2\frx332\fry330\move(514,822,514,476,0,1723)}回日本也別忘記我們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.81,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord0\1c&H8A898D&\move(514,476,514,412,0,599)\frz329.2\frx332\fry330}回日本也別忘記我們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這面旗是你們親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主賓到場啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來這裡排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 好看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們果然是母女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑起來跟你媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了怎麼了 她失戀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從某方面來說也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪方面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請用想像力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照理說我們要舉行過冬交接儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但這次沒有要交接的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以改為夏季隊回國典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接著交給隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有人都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今早天氣晴朗 是個適合旅行的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本次觀測之行特殊在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本首次有女高中生觀測隊員參與了南極生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是次巨大的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們肯定都心懷不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我們也極度不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她們證明了自己是優秀的觀測隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我甚至能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有男隊員不希望她們回去的吵鬧心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她們幾個要回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還請放棄妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後我想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感謝大家一路的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你們回國 也希望偶爾能回憶起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遙遠的天邊 在漆黑中默默過冬的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}願我們將來在這裡重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:08.64,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs20\1c&H170F0C&\frz357.6\pos(316,264)\frx352\fry4}飛鳥站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:08.64,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H2A160D&\frx352\fry4\pos(312,416)\frz2.901}東京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:08.64,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H331B12&\frx352\fry4\frz2.901\pos(138,454)}費利曼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來有請 夏季隊代表的小淵澤報瀨講話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各位 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想必各位都知道 我的媽媽是南極觀測隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她最喜歡的就是南極
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著迷戀南極而離開了家的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我對南極並沒有什麼好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想改變這種情緒 才來到了這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「比宇宙更遠的地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該說 我的母親是這麼稱呼這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這裡 一切都毫無保留
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無論時間 生物 還是內心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡沒有什麼能保護我們 沒有地方能躲藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的一切羞澀 與想掩蓋的心事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都在這裡嶄露無遺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於能帶著眼淚 與真實的自己坦誠相見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後和大家一同跨越難關 堅持到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}於是我才明白 媽媽愛著這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不僅是因為景色 天空與習習涼風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她同樣愛著與夥伴一同跨越困境的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她愛的是這片不受外界影響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}任何困難都只能和同伴一同跨越的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也愛上了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請努力過冬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定會回到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:51.47,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}深夜零時の地平線　広がる世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:55.85,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}今日がずっと眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:06.49,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}鼻の奥がツンとした　きれいできれいで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:11.08,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}胸が痛くなるほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:20.75,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}両手いっぱいありったけの人に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:31.55,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}意味なんかないって言われ続けたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:44.15,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}宇宙(そら)から届くひかり　逆さまの星空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.74,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}見果てぬ世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:55.87,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}勇気出して　進んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:31.66,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}宇宙(そら)より遠い場所で　真っ白な世界を見渡して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:35.66,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}ここから始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:44.29,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}さあ前を向いて　間違いなかったんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:50.55,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}言ってやるんだ　この思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:59.02,InSong2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}勇気出して　進んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:51.47,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}眼前是深夜零點的地平線 一片廣大的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:55.85,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}今天一直是那麼耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:06.49,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}我激動得鼻尖一癢 眼前的景象是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:11.08,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}燦爛到叫我心口作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:20.75,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}許許多多的人 裝滿雙手也擠不下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:31.55,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}都在勸我不要白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:44.15,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}只是仰頭看見那顛倒的星空 灑下的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.74,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}斑斕神秘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:55.87,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}只要拿出勇氣 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:31.66,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}在比宇宙更遠的地方 遙望這片雪白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:35.66,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}我會從這裡揚帆起航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:44.29,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}睜大眼睛直視前方 大聲喊出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:50.55,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}「我的執著沒有錯誤！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:59.02,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}拿出勇氣 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是些剩的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能幫我送給 在日本等我的阿優嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你酒臭味好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別介意 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 別忘了道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了啦 你快上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是結月的簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很有偶像風範
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賣掉多少張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們別嘰嘰喳喳的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會期待電視劇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然得回國再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來還有人在期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你得加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是時候出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才要向你們道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得一開始 我在廂型車裡說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時候跟你們聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我鼓起了莫大的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著你們的臉蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就覺得這個企劃絕對不能中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來一開始可能中止嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做大人的 該誠實的時刻就會說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長就麻煩你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會關心人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都上機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不留她下來過冬 媽媽會生我的氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就算沒有這個 也不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平均年齡馬上就升上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 接下來時間就長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:06.38,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっと記した夢　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:17.09,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:25.77,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:31.19,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:39.12,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:45.71,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:50.09,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:54.67,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:59.85,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:09.31,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:15.19,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南風はやがて島を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:19.74,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:31.25,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:35.76,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:40.47,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:45.47,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}進んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.90,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:06.38,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷記下了夢想 卻只找了一堆藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:17.09,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己總是忘記夢想 就怕去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:25.77,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什麼事 怕有什麼變故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:31.19,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但駐足不前 就什麼都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:39.12,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 邁出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:45.71,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:50.09,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:54.67,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:59.85,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:09.31,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紅紅的一輪夕陽 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:15.19,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南風跨越萬千島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:19.74,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹動起我的髮梢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:31.25,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:35.76,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:40.47,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波濤之中舉杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:45.47,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}繼續一步步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:49.90,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.50,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\fs25\1c&H3E456F&\be1\move(130.8,444,153.6,404,36,2706)\frx344\fry336\frz344.6}寄件備份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛來的時候還覺得好遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旅行就是這樣子的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這還不是結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有60度 50度 40度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定又要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算再吐幾次 再覺得難受得想死 也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無所謂 這也是旅行的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不覺得我們變堅強了點？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也可能是變隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這裡的一切都很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要穿成這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後的機會了 當然要把這身穿整齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看一下 亮眼睿智激…激動人心的報導也是最後的…
