Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:08.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\fs35}穿過紛擾的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:14.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\fs35}跨過日常的高牆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:18.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\fs35}如果跌跤出的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:27.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\fs35}都能顯得那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:51.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\fs35}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
